        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>COVID-19 Treatment Coverage Act</b><br> <br> This bill eliminates cost-sharing for items and services related to the treatment of COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019), including such services for uninsured individuals.</p>]]></text>
